        "timestamp": "2022-11-16 17:44:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n> \n> The original robot install script is being deleted, but the job definitions are still calling to include the file.\n> \n> If you want to delete this file, then my recommendation is to just replace the contents of it with the added py3 version and leave the job definition alone instead of adding the new install definition.\n\nI'm not removing the original, but I am renaming the new script I introduced recently, as Toine expressed a preference for making it clear the new version was designed for python3.",
